channel.title: Other server help
channel.description:
When i try to play on other peoples server that box comes up then automaticly shuts what can i do? Do i ahve to install something please help thanks!
The confused, :confused: :confused: :confused: :confused: pokemondner

item.title: Other server help
item.dc:creator: @bengina bengina
item.description:
@bengina wrote:

If it closes to quickly make sure that:

You have java installed
If your running vista to have a path to system32 in your enviromental variables

If that still doesnt work then:
Open a command prompt and run from there by typing in the location of the run_ client- this will not automatically close so then you can see an error if one appears.

Hope this helps
